result.name: Dumpling House

reviews.text: Excellent dumplings! The soup is tasty. Be prepared to wait for at least half an hour.

Haven’t visited the shop for quite a while.  Came again and still saw ‘people mountain people sea’.  Price didn’t change a lot but with more new variety of dumplings.  For classic dumplings, it’s $36 for 6 and $40 for 8 pcs.  
Price of other dumplings varies from $44 to $52 for 8 pcs.  Mix of multiple dumpling types add $4 to $8.  Overall, dumplings and the soup tasted the same.   Only one observation was that the dumpling size is much bigger than before.  With much more ingredients specially the vegetables portion but not the meat.  Overall the CP is still high but the quality is not of refinement.  It suits as a good meal rather than food of delicacy.

Delicious dumplings at reasonable price. The restaurant is pretty small and very crowded, and a long queue outside always. At least wait for 15mins but worth for waiting! Curry pork flavor and bell pepper pork flavor are recommended.
Double the size of the shop but still long queue to have yummy dumplings. The best dumplings in town for myself. The soup is sweet and fresh. Each dumpling is as big as my ✊ fist.
The dumplings are sooooooo big!!! They provided almost 13 flavors of dumplings. Also, their soup is very delicious too.

result.name: 餃子屋專門店

reviews.text: 從未試咁差。六隻煎饺半數爆開一小角 ，又唔脆，顔色只淺黄不似往日金黃或褐色，一D都唔乾身，餡只温熱，麵湯還比它熱。要多D菜甫唔啋人！問多兩次話要收多$2先有！服務差！真想反問若有客唔要菜甫有冇得倒轉頭減$2！

餃子味道水準比頭兩次食不斷下降
座位狹窄 坐得不舒服
生意比開業初好 店員服務態度愈來愈差..
不會再光顧
我覺得幾好食都係假 要等半個鐘以上 不過提提各位 早上11點開門時間最少人 如果心思思想一試的朋友 不妨早上來！
其實係咪好食就見人見智 水餃係大隻同多料既但用既料係一般，勝在大隻就沒有其他特別，人多地方又壁出入經常撞到人，工作阿姐又做到目無表情，如果排長龍真係唔值得等，好食又正宗既餃子店多的是。

份量很大但煎餃湯汁不夠,調味一般,米線和湯十分普通太軟且不夠濃。
環境地方很擠上菜也很慢。
唯一可取的是價錢還是比較相宜,路過不用等的話還是可以填填肚子,但專門等位就不必了。
